Slovenia ' s BTC to raise its equity . Slovenian warehouse and shopping centre operator BTC said on Thursday it would raise its equity capital by 1 . 83 billion tolars to 6 . 64 billion tolars . The company said in a statement it would issue 229 , 267 ordinary shares with a nominal value of 8 , 000 tolars each , extending the number of its shares to 830 , 000 . BTC said it expects to issue new shares in June and sell them to a limited number of subscribers , but gave no further details . - - Marja Novak , Ljubljana newsroom , 386 - 61 - 125 - 8439 
